				\usepackage{upgreek}
				\setlength{\oddsidemargin}{-69pt}
				\begin{document}$$\bar 3$$\end{document}m, Pnma, R3c, and R3m space groups are all adopted as the initial N(CH3)4SnI3 structures in the present study and denoted as 3D-cubic structures. For the ABX3 perovskites with large A cations (e.g., BaMnO3), the hexagonal structure with the space group P63/mmc had also been reported, so the P63/mmc structure is also adopted as an initial structure of N(CH3)4SnI3 and denoted as 3D-hex in Fig. 1f.

